<P>MEMOIRS OF THE Court of <HI>France</HI> AND City of <HI>Paris:</HI> CONTAINING The Intrigues of that <HI>Court,</HI> and the Characters of the <HI>Mini&s;ters of State,</HI> and other <HI>Officers</HI>; Together With the Occurrences of the TOWN.</P>
